{
  "id": "adv_card_aoi_01_01",
  "title": "井川葵 1話 僕は僕",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――時は遡り",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Turning back the clock…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.43333333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――NEXT VENUSグランプリの予選を控えたある日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—One day‚ ahead of the preliminary round\nof the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.9333333333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-close-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3766.6666666666665,
          "startTime": 5.7
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 5.066666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "やあ、この間ぶりだね\n三枝さんとこの新米プロデューサーくん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ nice seeing you again.\nRookie producer from Saegusa-san’s agency.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "先日はありがとう\n新米なのは正しいけどマネージャーなんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks for the other day.\nI may be a rookie‚ but I’m a manager not a producer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.633333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 15.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "肩書きなんてどうでもいいよ\nレッスン場使わせてもらうよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Never mind your title.\nI’m going to use the lesson studio.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.433333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、まだウチの子達が使ってて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ my girls are still in there…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.166666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 21.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "隅っこで勝手にやってるから\n気にしないでいいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll just use the corner.\nDon’t mind me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "LizNoirの井川葵が練習してるのに\n気にしない訳ないだろう？　もうちょっと待ってくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course they’ll mind if Aoi Igawa from LizNoir\nis practicing next to them. Please‚ they’ll be done in a bit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 30.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "大げさだなぁ\nじゃあ外でやってるから空いたら教えてくれる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Overreacting.\nFine‚ I’ll warm up outside. Let me know when the studio is free.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 34.93333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "路上でダンスの練習をするつもりか！？\nやめてくれ、もっと大騒ぎになる！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re going to dance in the middle of the street?!\nThat’s going to be ten times worse!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 40.13333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "僕は別に気にしないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not for me. I don’t care.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "昔からその辺で踊っていたしね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I used to dance around here all time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 44.06666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "君の事務所の人が気にするに決まってるだろ！？\nほら、大人しくコーヒーでも飲んで待っててくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I bet the people from your agency care!\nHere‚ have some coffee and don’t make a fuss.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.233333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 50.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "他の事務所のアイドルなのに\n君はおせっかいだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not even with your agency.\nNo need for you to take care of me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.833333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 55.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "ん……\nちょっと温いよ、これ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmmm.\nThis is kinda lukewarm.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 59.96666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ごめん\n自分で飲むつもりで買って忘れてたやつだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry.\nI was going to drink it myself and then forgot about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "まあ、胃に入れれば一緒だしね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ who cares once it’s inside your stomach‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 67.23333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "――っくん、ごちそうさま",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*glug* Thanks for the drink.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 69.83333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "君は少し変わった子だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re a little weird‚ aren’t you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "よく言われるよ\nでも僕は僕以外の人にはなれない、これからもね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I get that a lot.\nBut I am me. I can only be me‚ now and forever.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 78.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（井川葵――十七歳にしてダンスも歌も）\n（同世代アイドル達より数歩前を行く実力者だ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Aoi Igawa. At just 17‚ her singing and dancing)\n(are already a few steps ahead of idols her own age.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 85.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（けど、あまりに自由奔放で大御所の芸能人に対しても）\n（物怖じしなかったり、危ない所もあるらしい）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(But she’s a little too free-spirited‚ and doesn’t)\n(respect the industry chain of command.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 93.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "たいていの人は君みたいに\n自信を持って生きてはいないんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There aren’t many people who can live their lives\nwith the kind of confidence you show.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 97.86666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "どうして？\n自信なんて自分で勝手に持てばいいじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why ever not?\nConfidence is easy. Just decide to have it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 101.86666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "正論ではあるけど実績がないとね\nその年齢で君ほどの実績がある子はそういない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s true‚ but you need results to back it up.\nThere aren’t many girls your age who have accomplished so much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 108.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_01-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "僕は実績なんて関係ないと思う\n結果はどうあれ努力を積み上げてきたことは事実なんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t think results really matter.\nHard work isn’t diminished by how things turn out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
